                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "谜影障身法"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">风元素伤害</span>，召唤<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">惊奇猫猫盒</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/20/157749474/b718fd9ceee2d78fdf5d76f345458f71_7573299953943563308.png",
                "id": "talent6232",
                "key": "魔术·运变惊奇",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "魔术·运变惊奇"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结束阶段：</span>造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素伤害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：2</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">我方出战角色受到伤害时：</span>抵消1点伤害。（每回合1次）</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">我方角色受到</span><span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">冰</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">/</span><span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">水</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">/</span><span style=\"color: #FF9999\">火</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">/</span><span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">雷</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">/伤害时：</span>转换此牌的元素类型，改为造成所受到的元素类型的伤害。（离场前仅限一次）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/20/157749474/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_5587904716443173551.png",
                "id": "talent27139",
                "key": "惊奇猫猫盒",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/20/157749474/bc84abe7e3d8d79c9b75a0de329313dc_3607328320671802671.png",
                "title": "惊奇猫猫盒"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>和已附着的元素发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">扩散（冰）</span>：对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点冰伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">扩散（水）</span>：对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点水伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">扩散（火）</span>：对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点火伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">扩散（雷）</span>：对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点雷伤害</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/20/157749474/c97292d96456bfe4abeca16bfce801e4_6385667664802096101.png",
                "id": "talent98290",
